Adding a new user:
analyst@94caf7cb696a:~$ sudo useradd researcher9
Adding user to group:
analyst@94caf7cb696a:~$ sudo usermod -g research_team researcher9
Making the user the owner of a file:
analyst@94caf7cb696a:~$ sudo chown researcher9 /home/researcher2/projects/project_r.txt
Adding the user to a secondary group:
analyst@94caf7cb696a:~$ sudo usermod -a -G sales_team researcher9
Deleting the user:
analyst@94caf7cb696a:~$ sudo userdel researcher9
userdel: group researcher9 not removed because it is not the primary group of user researcher9.
Clean up the user group:
analyst@94caf7cb696a:~$ sudo groupdel researcher9

